{
  "video_id": "dYNc3P4j-t4",
  "title": "The world doesn't need more nuclear weapons | Erika Gregory",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12714.0,
      "end_time": 16282.0,
      "text": "Let me ask you all a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16282.0,
      "end_time": 20170.0,
      "text": "How much weapons-grade nuclear material do you think it would take"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20170.0,
      "end_time": 23554.0,
      "text": "to level a city the size of San Francisco?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23554.0,
      "end_time": 25610.0,
      "text": "How many of you think it would be an amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25610.0,
      "end_time": 29685.0,
      "text": "about the size of this suitcase?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29685.0,
      "end_time": 34327.0,
      "text": "OK. And how about this minibus?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34327.0,
      "end_time": 35504.0,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35504.0,
      "end_time": 38222.0,
      "text": "Well actually, under the right circumstances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38222.0,
      "end_time": 43697.0,
      "text": "an amount of highly enriched uranium about the size of your morning latte"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43697.0,
      "end_time": 46639.0,
      "text": "would be enough to kill 100,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46639.0,
      "end_time": 48522.0,
      "text": "instantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48522.0,
      "end_time": 52616.0,
      "text": "Hundreds of thousands of others would become horribly ill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52616.0,
      "end_time": 55665.0,
      "text": "and parts of the city would be uninhabitable for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55665.0,
      "end_time": 57993.0,
      "text": "if not for decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57993.0,
      "end_time": 60580.0,
      "text": "But you can forget that nuclear latte,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60580.0,
      "end_time": 66574.0,
      "text": "because today&#39;s nuclear weapons are hundreds of times more powerful"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66574.0,
      "end_time": 70891.0,
      "text": "even than those we dropped on Hiroshima and Nagasaki."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70891.0,
      "end_time": 76234.0,
      "text": "And even a limited nuclear war involving, say, tens of nuclear weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76234.0,
      "end_time": 81609.0,
      "text": "could lead to the end of all life on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81609.0,
      "end_time": 84907.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s really important that you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84907.0,
      "end_time": 90012.0,
      "text": "that right now we have over 15,000 nuclear weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90012.0,
      "end_time": 92251.0,
      "text": "in the hands of nine nations."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92251.0,
      "end_time": 96904.0,
      "text": "And if you live in a city or near a military facility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96904.0,
      "end_time": 100523.0,
      "text": "one is likely pointed right at you."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 100523.0,
      "end_time": 103438.0,
      "text": "In fact, if you live in any of the rural areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103438.0,
      "end_time": 105944.0,
      "text": "where nuclear weapons are stored globally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105944.0,
      "end_time": 108188.0,
      "text": "one is likely pointed at you."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108188.0,
      "end_time": 112694.0,
      "text": "About 1,800 of these weapons are on high alert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112694.0,
      "end_time": 116408.0,
      "text": "which means they can be launched within 15 minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 116408.0,
      "end_time": 120228.0,
      "text": "of a presidential command."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 120228.0,
      "end_time": 123819.0,
      "text": "So I know this is a bummer of an issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 123819.0,
      "end_time": 126656.0,
      "text": "and maybe you have that -- what was it? -- psychic fatigue"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 126656.0,
      "end_time": 128745.0,
      "text": "that we heard about a little bit earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 128745.0,
      "end_time": 131072.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to switch gears for just a second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 131072.0,
      "end_time": 133482.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to talk about my imaginary friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 133482.0,
      "end_time": 136292.0,
      "text": "who I like to think of as Jasmine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 136292.0,
      "end_time": 137662.0,
      "text": "just for a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 137662.0,
      "end_time": 140203.0,
      "text": "Jasmine, at the age of 25,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 140203.0,
      "end_time": 144582.0,
      "text": "is part of a generation that is more politically and socially engaged"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144582.0,
      "end_time": 147011.0,
      "text": "than anything we&#39;ve seen in 50 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 147011.0,
      "end_time": 148974.0,
      "text": "She and her friends think of themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 148974.0,
      "end_time": 152247.0,
      "text": "as change agents and leaders and activists."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 152247.0,
      "end_time": 156317.0,
      "text": "I think of them as Generation Possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 156317.0,
      "end_time": 159422.0,
      "text": "They regularly protest about the issues they care about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159422.0,
      "end_time": 162854.0,
      "text": "but nuclear weapons are not one of them, which makes sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 162854.0,
      "end_time": 167076.0,
      "text": "because Jasmine was born in 1991, at the end of the Cold War."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167076.0,
      "end_time": 170206.0,
      "text": "So she didn&#39;t grow up hearing a lot about nuclear weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170206.0,
      "end_time": 173813.0,
      "text": "She never had to duck and cover under her desk at school."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173813.0,
      "end_time": 178128.0,
      "text": "For Jasmine, a fallout shelter is an app in the Android store."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 178128.0,
      "end_time": 180847.0,
      "text": "Nuclear weapons help win games."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180847.0,
      "end_time": 183305.0,
      "text": "And that is really a shame,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183305.0,
      "end_time": 186603.0,
      "text": "because right now, we need Generation Possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 186603.0,
      "end_time": 191545.0,
      "text": "to help us make some really important decisions about nuclear weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 191545.0,
      "end_time": 198005.0,
      "text": "For instance, will we further reduce our nuclear arsenals globally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 198005.0,
      "end_time": 200945.0,
      "text": "or will we spend billions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 200945.0,
      "end_time": 203192.0,
      "text": "maybe a trillion dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 203192.0,
      "end_time": 206538.0,
      "text": "to modernize them so they last throughout the 21st century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 206538.0,
      "end_time": 209861.0,
      "text": "so that by the time Jasmine is my age, she&#39;s talking to her children"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 209861.0,
      "end_time": 211816.0,
      "text": "and maybe even her grandchildren"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 211816.0,
      "end_time": 215098.0,
      "text": "about the threat of nuclear holocaust?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215098.0,
      "end_time": 218028.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re paying any attention at all to cyberthreats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218028.0,
      "end_time": 222019.0,
      "text": "or, for instance, if you&#39;ve read about the Stuxnet virus"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 222019.0,
      "end_time": 225908.0,
      "text": "or, for God&#39;s sake, if you&#39;ve ever had an email account or a Yahoo account"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 225908.0,
      "end_time": 227980.0,
      "text": "or a phone hacked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 227980.0,
      "end_time": 232156.0,
      "text": "you can imagine the whole new world of hurt that could be triggered"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 232156.0,
      "end_time": 235944.0,
      "text": "by modernization in a period of cyberwarfare."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235944.0,
      "end_time": 238185.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re paying attention to the money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 238185.0,
      "end_time": 241270.0,
      "text": "a trillion dollars could go a long way"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241270.0,
      "end_time": 244137.0,
      "text": "to feeding and educating and employing people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244137.0,
      "end_time": 248691.0,
      "text": "all of which could reduce the threat of nuclear war to begin with."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248691.0,
      "end_time": 249869.0,
      "text": "So --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 249869.0,
      "end_time": 252915.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 252915.0,
      "end_time": 255392.0,
      "text": "This is really crucial right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 255392.0,
      "end_time": 259274.0,
      "text": "because nuclear weapons -- they&#39;re vulnerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259274.0,
      "end_time": 260885.0,
      "text": "We have solid evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 260885.0,
      "end_time": 264551.0,
      "text": "that terrorists are trying to get ahold of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264551.0,
      "end_time": 265896.0,
      "text": "Just this last spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 265896.0,
      "end_time": 270626.0,
      "text": "when four retirees and two taxi drivers were arrested"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270626.0,
      "end_time": 272249.0,
      "text": "in the Republic of Georgia"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 272249.0,
      "end_time": 275998.0,
      "text": "for trying to sell nuclear materials for 200 million dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 275998.0,
      "end_time": 280111.0,
      "text": "they demonstrated that the black market for this stuff is alive and well."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280111.0,
      "end_time": 281396.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s really important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 281396.0,
      "end_time": 285217.0,
      "text": "because there have been dozens of accidents"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 285217.0,
      "end_time": 286522.0,
      "text": "involving nuclear weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 286522.0,
      "end_time": 289587.0,
      "text": "and I bet most of us have never heard anything about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 289587.0,
      "end_time": 291153.0,
      "text": "Just here in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 291153.0,
      "end_time": 295203.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve dropped nuclear weapons on the Carolinas twice."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295203.0,
      "end_time": 297553.0,
      "text": "In one case, one of the bombs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297553.0,
      "end_time": 299749.0,
      "text": "which fell out of an Air Force plane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 299749.0,
      "end_time": 300972.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t detonate"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 300972.0,
      "end_time": 304109.0,
      "text": "because the nuclear core was stored somewhere else on the plane."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 304109.0,
      "end_time": 308169.0,
      "text": "In another case, the weapon did arm when it hit the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 308169.0,
      "end_time": 312935.0,
      "text": "and five of the switches designed to keep it from detonating failed."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 312935.0,
      "end_time": 315521.0,
      "text": "Luckily, the sixth one didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 315521.0,
      "end_time": 318973.0,
      "text": "But if that&#39;s not enough to get your attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 318973.0,
      "end_time": 322655.0,
      "text": "there was the 1995 Black Brant incident."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 322655.0,
      "end_time": 324958.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when Russian radar technicians saw"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 324958.0,
      "end_time": 327501.0,
      "text": "what they thought was a US nuclear missile"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 327501.0,
      "end_time": 330172.0,
      "text": "streaking towards Russian airspace."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 330172.0,
      "end_time": 332916.0,
      "text": "It later turned out to be a Norwegian rocket"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 332916.0,
      "end_time": 335522.0,
      "text": "collecting data about the northern lights."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 335522.0,
      "end_time": 336700.0,
      "text": "But at that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 336700.0,
      "end_time": 340495.0,
      "text": "Russian President Boris Yeltsin came within five minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340495.0,
      "end_time": 344671.0,
      "text": "of launching a full-scale retaliatory nuclear attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344671.0,
      "end_time": 348924.0,
      "text": "against the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 348924.0,
      "end_time": 352990.0,
      "text": "So, most of the world&#39;s nuclear nations"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 352990.0,
      "end_time": 357352.0,
      "text": "have committed to getting rid of these weapons of mass destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 357352.0,
      "end_time": 359835.0,
      "text": "But consider this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 359835.0,
      "end_time": 363183.0,
      "text": "the Treaty on the Non-Proliferation of Nuclear Weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 363183.0,
      "end_time": 366644.0,
      "text": "which is the most widely adopted arms control treaty in history"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 366644.0,
      "end_time": 369398.0,
      "text": "with 190 signatories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 369398.0,
      "end_time": 374716.0,
      "text": "sets no specific date by which the world&#39;s nuclear-armed nations"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 374716.0,
      "end_time": 377692.0,
      "text": "will get rid of their nuclear weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 377692.0,
      "end_time": 380486.0,
      "text": "Now, when John F. Kennedy sent a man to the moon"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380486.0,
      "end_time": 383681.0,
      "text": "and decided to bring him back, or decided to do both those things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383681.0,
      "end_time": 386625.0,
      "text": "he didn&#39;t say, &quot;Hey, whenever you guys get to it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 386625.0,
      "end_time": 388656.0,
      "text": "He gave us a deadline."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 388656.0,
      "end_time": 390502.0,
      "text": "He gave us a challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 390502.0,
      "end_time": 394033.0,
      "text": "that would have been incredible just a few years earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394033.0,
      "end_time": 395559.0,
      "text": "And with that challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 395559.0,
      "end_time": 398458.0,
      "text": "he inspired scientists and marketers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398458.0,
      "end_time": 401152.0,
      "text": "astronauts and schoolteachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 401152.0,
      "end_time": 403928.0,
      "text": "He gave us a vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 403928.0,
      "end_time": 405927.0,
      "text": "But along with that vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 405927.0,
      "end_time": 409495.0,
      "text": "he also tried to give us -- and most people don&#39;t know this, either --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 409495.0,
      "end_time": 411503.0,
      "text": "he tried to give us a partner"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 411503.0,
      "end_time": 416948.0,
      "text": "in the form of our fiercest Cold War rival, the Soviet Union."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 416948.0,
      "end_time": 420006.0,
      "text": "Because part of Kennedy&#39;s vision for the Apollo program"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 420006.0,
      "end_time": 423817.0,
      "text": "was that it be a cooperation, not a competition, with the Soviets."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 423817.0,
      "end_time": 428007.0,
      "text": "And apparently, Nikita Khrushchev, the Soviet Premier, agreed."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 428007.0,
      "end_time": 431347.0,
      "text": "But before that cooperation could be realized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 431347.0,
      "end_time": 433042.0,
      "text": "Kennedy was assassinated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 433042.0,
      "end_time": 436581.0,
      "text": "and that part of the vision was deferred."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 436581.0,
      "end_time": 441784.0,
      "text": "But the promise of joint innovation between these two nuclear superpowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 441784.0,
      "end_time": 444305.0,
      "text": "wasn&#39;t totally extinguished."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 444305.0,
      "end_time": 448222.0,
      "text": "Because in 1991, which is the year that Jasmine was born"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 448222.0,
      "end_time": 450732.0,
      "text": "and the Soviet Union fell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 450732.0,
      "end_time": 453529.0,
      "text": "these two nations engaged in a project"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 453529.0,
      "end_time": 456110.0,
      "text": "that genuinely does seem incredible today"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 456110.0,
      "end_time": 458812.0,
      "text": "in the truest sense of that word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 458812.0,
      "end_time": 463432.0,
      "text": "which is that the US sent cash to the Russians when they needed it most,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 463432.0,
      "end_time": 466211.0,
      "text": "to secure loose nuclear materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 466211.0,
      "end_time": 469440.0,
      "text": "and to employ out-of-work nuclear scientists."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 469440.0,
      "end_time": 476167.0,
      "text": "They worked alongside American scientists to convert weapons-grade uranium"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 476167.0,
      "end_time": 480464.0,
      "text": "into the type of fuel that can be used for nuclear power instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 480464.0,
      "end_time": 484202.0,
      "text": "They called it, &quot;Megatons to Megawatts.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 484202.0,
      "end_time": 487362.0,
      "text": "So the result is that for over 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 487362.0,
      "end_time": 490193.0,
      "text": "our two nations had a program"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 490193.0,
      "end_time": 494030.0,
      "text": "that meant that one in 10 lightbulbs in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 494030.0,
      "end_time": 499530.0,
      "text": "was essentially fueled by former Russian warheads."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 499530.0,
      "end_time": 503905.0,
      "text": "So, together these two nations did something truly audacious."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 503905.0,
      "end_time": 507998.0,
      "text": "But the good news is, the global community has the chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 507998.0,
      "end_time": 512897.0,
      "text": "to do something just as audacious today."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 512897.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515448.00000000006,
      "text": "To get rid of nuclear weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 515448.0,
      "end_time": 520010.0,
      "text": "and to end the supply of the materials required to produce them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 520010.0,
      "end_time": 523219.0,
      "text": "some experts tell me would take 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 523219.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525710.0,
      "text": "It would take a renaissance of sorts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 525710.0,
      "end_time": 528149.0,
      "text": "the kinds of innovation that, for better or worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 528149.0,
      "end_time": 532147.0,
      "text": "underpinned both the Manhattan Project, which gave rise to nuclear weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 532147.0,
      "end_time": 535019.0,
      "text": "and the Megatons to Megawatts program."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 535019.0,
      "end_time": 537665.0,
      "text": "It would take design constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 537665.0,
      "end_time": 540407.0,
      "text": "These are fundamental to creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 540407.0,
      "end_time": 544447.0,
      "text": "things like a platform for international collaboration;"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 544447.0,
      "end_time": 548925.0,
      "text": "a date certain, which is a forcing mechanism;"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 548925.0,
      "end_time": 552735.0,
      "text": "and a positive vision that inspires action."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 552735.0,
      "end_time": 556468.0,
      "text": "It would take us to 2045."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 556468.0,
      "end_time": 560973.0,
      "text": "Now, 2045 happens to be the 100th anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 560973.0,
      "end_time": 565247.0,
      "text": "of the birth of nuclear weapons in the New Mexico desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 565247.0,
      "end_time": 568458.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s also an important date for another reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 568458.0,
      "end_time": 573011.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s predicted to be the advent of the singularity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 573011.0,
      "end_time": 575431.0,
      "text": "a new moment in human development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 575431.0,
      "end_time": 581106.0,
      "text": "where the lines between artificial intelligence and human intelligence blur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 581106.0,
      "end_time": 585559.0,
      "text": "where computing and consciousness become almost indistinguishable"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 585559.0,
      "end_time": 591215.0,
      "text": "and advanced technologies help us solve the 21st century&#39;s greatest problems:"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 591215.0,
      "end_time": 594133.0,
      "text": "hunger, energy, poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 594133.0,
      "end_time": 598318.0,
      "text": "ushering in an era of abundance."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 598318.0,
      "end_time": 599924.0,
      "text": "And we all get to go to space"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 599924.0,
      "end_time": 604039.0,
      "text": "on our way to becoming a multi-planetary species."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 604039.0,
      "end_time": 607915.0,
      "text": "Now, the people who really believe this vision are the first to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 607915.0,
      "end_time": 611618.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t yet know precisely how we&#39;re going to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 611618.0,
      "end_time": 614434.0,
      "text": "But the values behind their vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 614434.0,
      "end_time": 617789.0,
      "text": "and the willingness to ask &quot;How might we?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 617789.0,
      "end_time": 620884.0,
      "text": "have inspired a generation of innovators."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 620884.0,
      "end_time": 624380.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re working backward from the outcomes they want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 624380.0,
      "end_time": 628608.0,
      "text": "using the creative problem-solving methods of collaborative design."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 628608.0,
      "end_time": 630872.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re busting through obstacles."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 630872.0,
      "end_time": 635513.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re redefining what we all consider possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 635513.0,
      "end_time": 637706.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 637706.0,
      "end_time": 641940.0,
      "text": "that vision of abundance isn&#39;t compatible"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 641940.0,
      "end_time": 648169.0,
      "text": "with a world that still relies on a 20th-century nuclear doctrine"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 648169.0,
      "end_time": 652945.0,
      "text": "called &quot;mutually assured destruction.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 652945.0,
      "end_time": 658446.0,
      "text": "It has to be about building the foundations for the 22nd century."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 658446.0,
      "end_time": 664276.0,
      "text": "It has to be about strategies for mutually assured prosperity"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 664276.0,
      "end_time": 669175.0,
      "text": "or, at the very least, mutually assured survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 669175.0,
      "end_time": 674422.0,
      "text": "Now, every day, I get to meet people who are real pioneers"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 674422.0,
      "end_time": 676363.0,
      "text": "in the field of nuclear threats."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 676363.0,
      "end_time": 679888.0,
      "text": "As you can see, many of them are young women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 679888.0,
      "end_time": 682488.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re doing fiercely interesting stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 682488.0,
      "end_time": 687015.0,
      "text": "like Mareena Robinson Snowden here, who is developing new ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 687015.0,
      "end_time": 689701.0,
      "text": "better ways, to detect nuclear warheads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 689701.0,
      "end_time": 691948.0,
      "text": "which will help us overcome a critical hurdle"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 691948.0,
      "end_time": 693906.0,
      "text": "to international disarmament."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 693906.0,
      "end_time": 696799.0,
      "text": "Or Melissa Hanham, who is using satellite imaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 696799.0,
      "end_time": 701358.0,
      "text": "to make sense of what&#39;s going on around far-flung nuclear sites."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 701358.0,
      "end_time": 704079.0,
      "text": "Or we have Beatrice Fihn in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 704079.0,
      "end_time": 708376.0,
      "text": "who has been campaigning to make nuclear weapons illegal"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 708376.0,
      "end_time": 710084.0,
      "text": "in international courts of law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 710084.0,
      "end_time": 713000.0,
      "text": "and just won a big victory at the UN last week."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 713000.0,
      "end_time": 716202.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 716202.0,
      "end_time": 717942.0,
      "text": "And yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 717942.0,
      "end_time": 719797.0,
      "text": "and yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 719797.0,
      "end_time": 723239.0,
      "text": "with all of our talk in this culture about moon shots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 723239.0,
      "end_time": 727991.0,
      "text": "too few members of Generation Possible and those of us who mentor them"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 727991.0,
      "end_time": 730524.0,
      "text": "are taking on nuclear weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 730524.0,
      "end_time": 733898.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as if there&#39;s a taboo."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 733898.0,
      "end_time": 738597.0,
      "text": "But I remember something Kennedy said that has really stuck with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 738597.0,
      "end_time": 740379.0,
      "text": "and that is something to the effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 740379.0,
      "end_time": 742545.0,
      "text": "that humans can be as big as the solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 742545.0,
      "end_time": 744427.0,
      "text": "to all the problems we&#39;ve created."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 744427.0,
      "end_time": 747685.0,
      "text": "No problem of human destiny, he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 747685.0,
      "end_time": 751296.0,
      "text": "is beyond human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 751296.0,
      "end_time": 753376.0,
      "text": "I believe that."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 753376.0,
      "end_time": 756535.0,
      "text": "And I bet a lot of you here believe that, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 756535.0,
      "end_time": 760646.0,
      "text": "And I know Generation Possible believes it."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 760646.0,
      "end_time": 765183.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s time to commit to a date."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 765183.0,
      "end_time": 768735.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s end the nuclear weapons chapter"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 768735.0,
      "end_time": 773119.0,
      "text": "on the 100th anniversary of its inception."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 773119.0,
      "end_time": 777869.0,
      "text": "After all, by 2045, we will have held billions of people hostage"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 777869.0,
      "end_time": 780167.0,
      "text": "to the threat of nuclear annihilation."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 780167.0,
      "end_time": 783512.0,
      "text": "Surely, 100 years will have been enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 783512.0,
      "end_time": 787215.0,
      "text": "Surely, a century of economic development"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 787215.0,
      "end_time": 790634.0,
      "text": "and the development of military strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 790634.0,
      "end_time": 794802.0,
      "text": "will have given us better ways to manage global conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 794802.0,
      "end_time": 799759.0,
      "text": "Surely, if ever there was a global moon shot worth supporting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 799759.0,
      "end_time": 801846.0,
      "text": "this is it."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 801846.0,
      "end_time": 804484.0,
      "text": "Now, in the face of real threats --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 804484.0,
      "end_time": 807504.0,
      "text": "for instance, North Korea&#39;s recent nuclear weapons tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 807504.0,
      "end_time": 809808.0,
      "text": "which fly in the face of sanctions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 809808.0,
      "end_time": 812132.0,
      "text": "reasonable people disagree"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 812132.0,
      "end_time": 816055.0,
      "text": "about whether we should maintain some number of nuclear weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 816055.0,
      "end_time": 818550.0,
      "text": "to deter aggression."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 818550.0,
      "end_time": 822205.0,
      "text": "But the question is: What&#39;s the magic number?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 822205.0,
      "end_time": 824140.0,
      "text": "Is it a thousand?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 824140.0,
      "end_time": 827246.0,
      "text": "Is it a hundred? Ten?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 827246.0,
      "end_time": 829395.0,
      "text": "And then we have to ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 829395.0,
      "end_time": 832038.0,
      "text": "Who should be responsible for them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 832038.0,
      "end_time": 833920.0,
      "text": "I think we can agree, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 833920.0,
      "end_time": 837993.0,
      "text": "that having 15,000 of them represents a greater global threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 837993.0,
      "end_time": 841184.0,
      "text": "to Jasmine&#39;s generation than a promise."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 841184.0,
      "end_time": 844366.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s time we make a promise"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 844366.0,
      "end_time": 847103.0,
      "text": "of a world in which we&#39;ve broken the stranglehold"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 847103.0,
      "end_time": 850625.0,
      "text": "that nuclear weapons have on our imaginations;"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 850625.0,
      "end_time": 853261.0,
      "text": "in which we invest in the creative solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 853261.0,
      "end_time": 857015.0,
      "text": "that come from working backward from the future we desperately want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 857015.0,
      "end_time": 859573.0,
      "text": "rather than plodding forward from a present"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 859573.0,
      "end_time": 864392.0,
      "text": "that brings all of the mental models and biases of the past with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 864392.0,
      "end_time": 869718.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s time we pledge our resources as leaders across the spectrum"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 869718.0,
      "end_time": 873146.0,
      "text": "to work on this old problem in new ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 873146.0,
      "end_time": 876001.0,
      "text": "to ask, &quot;How might we?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 876001.0,
      "end_time": 878328.0,
      "text": "How might we make good on a promise"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 878328.0,
      "end_time": 881929.0,
      "text": "of greater security for Jasmine&#39;s generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 881929.0,
      "end_time": 886116.0,
      "text": "in a world beyond nuclear weapons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 886116.0,
      "end_time": 889782.0,
      "text": "I truly hope you will join us."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 889782.0,
      "end_time": 890969.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 890969.0,
      "end_time": 894295.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 894295.0,
      "end_time": 895992.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 895992.0,
      "end_time": 905992.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}